snippet.title: Don't do STUNTS if you know you will FAIL - Funniest FAIL COLLECTION!
snippet.description:
Not everyone is for everything :D Some of us are more agile, some of us are less. Try to not do stunts if you know you might fail, as you may end up injured. Take care of yourselves, guys :D So ridiculous and funny!  What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
